  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U vreme <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect</span>, možete skratiti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have</span> u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">'ve</span> nakon <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">you</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">they</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">has</span> u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">'s</span> nakon <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">it</span>. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I've walked to the park.</span> - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I've</span> je skraćenica za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I have</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She's seen the movie.</span> - <span class=\"highlighted-text\">She's</span> je skraćenica od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she has</span>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
